posting_body: ['Schedule a Tour Today: <URL>', 'Discover a life of ease at Palmetto Promenade.', 'At our luxury apartments in Boca Raton, residents will find a selection of one bedroom, two bedroom, and three bedroom homes that are sure to suit any lifestyle.', 'In each home, residents will enjoy the chef-caliber kitchens with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances, private balconies, and spacious closets with built-in shelving.', 'Throughout the community at our Boca apartments, residents can take advantage of the resort-style swimming pool with private cabanas, cutting-edge fitness center, and the outdoor entertainment area.', 'Amenities:', '-Powder rooms in select residences', '-Additional premium storage space available', '-Porcelain tile tub and shower surrounds', '-Washer and dryer in every residence', '-Professional concierge services available', '-Community room, business center, Wi-Fi lounge', '-Wood flooring throughout the kitchen, living and dining areas', '-Cutting edge fitness studio with cardio, strength training, Fitness On Demand and yoga studio', '-Resort-style landscaping and water features surround the community', '-Ceiling fans included', '-Stylish private cabanas', '-Summer kitchen pavilion including grills, pizza oven and refrigeration', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
